<h2 class="rm-manual">Culture</h2>
<h1 href="https://mashable.com/2018/06/12/trump-us-north-korea-summit/">Watch Kim Jong-un's stunned reaction to Trump's fat joke</h1>
<p class="rm-manual"> Image: kevin lim/the strait times/handout/Getty Images </p>
<p class="rm-manual"><span><span>By <a href="file:///author/heather-dockray/">Heather Dockray</a></span>2018-06-12 09:27:00 UTC</span></p>
<p>Most people wouldn't use an international nuclear weapons summit to try out their latest comedy material.</p>
<p>Most people aren't President Trump.</p>
<p>At lunchtime during Trump's Singapore summit Tuesday, the president 
joked to photographers that they should make him and Kim Jong-un look 
"handsome and thin."</p>
<p class="rm-manual">SEE ALSO: <a href="https://mashable.com/2018/06/07/how-to-talk-to-kids-about-pride-lgbtq-identity/">5 ways parents can talk to kids about LGBTQ identity</a></p>
<p>“Getting a good picture everybody? So we look nice and handsome and thin? Perfect,” Trump joked.</p>
<p>Watch the North Korean leader's reaction:</p>
<p>Translators are available on the summit, so it doesn't appear that 
Kim Jong-un missed the joke. In the past, Trump has called the North 
Korean leader "short and fat" in a tweet.</p>
<p>In other words ... I never thought I would have anything in common with a <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2018/06/11/world/asia/north-korea-human-rights.html">spectacularly violent</a>,
 brutally oppressive North Korean dictator who starves his own people, 
but I was glad we could share this join moment of horror together.</p>
<p>Progress, people!</p>
